data.description: **Ask me how you can buy this house with NO MONEY DOWN!!**OPEN HOUSE - Saturday, January 13, 12:00 noon to 2:00 p.m.** Introducing a charming residence situated at 104 N Queen St, nestled in the quaint town of Littlestown, PA. This inviting home features a broad living space, perfectly laid out on a sizable parcel of land. It houses four ample bedrooms, where three have en suite full bathrooms, providing ultimate privacy and ease.   Upon entering this home, you are welcomed by an updated kitchen that combines modern functionality with elegant aesthetics. The kitchen features high-quality granite countertops that add a touch of sophistication to the space.  The property also offers ample outdoor space with a large yard perfect for outdoor activities or simply enjoying a beautiful day. In addition to this, there is off-street parking available for your convenience. To further enhance the charm of this home, there is a covered front porch where you can relax and enjoy your surroundings.  One of the key advantages of this property is its location. It's just a short walk into the town of Littlestown, making it easy to access local amenities and services. Littlestown has much to offer residents - from its charming downtown area brimming with shops and restaurants to its close-knit community atmosphere.  In terms of recreational opportunities, Littlestown boasts numerous parks and green spaces for outdoor enthusiasts, as well as cultural attractions such as museums and art galleries. Educational facilities in the area are highly regarded and healthcare facilities are easily accessible.  This home provides an excellent opportunity for those who appreciate quality living spaces combined with the convenience of being close to town amenities. Whether you're seeking comfort inside or looking forward to exploring what Littlestown has to offer outside, this property could be an ideal fit for your lifestyle needs.
